      "name": "9. Charts — Intraday",
      "description": "Intraday OHLCV candle data. Intervals: 1, 5, 15, 25, 60 minutes.\n\nDate format: YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss\nMax range: ~90 days\n\n**IMPORTANT:** The securityId must match the exchangeSegment and instrument.\n- NSE Equity: exchangeSegment=NSE_EQ, instrument=EQUITY\n- NSE Index: exchangeSegment=IDX_I, instrument=INDEX\n- NSE F&O: exchangeSegment=NSE_FNO, instrument=FUTIDX/OPTIDX/FUTSTK/OPTSTK\n- MCX: exchangeSegment=MCX_COMM, instrument=FUTCOM/OPTFUT",
      "item": [
